      • run

        public void run()

        Run operation on this object.

        This method will perform the following actions:
        1. Cast getObject() into the appropriate number of Record and Param[] instances
        2. Call getIntProperty("command")
        3. If command is COMMAND_STORE_RECORD Then call Record.store(TableDataSource).
        4. Else If command is COMMAND_DELETE_RECORD Then call Record.store(TableDataSource).
        5. Else If command is COMMAND_INSERT_RECORD Then call Table.insert(Param[]).
        6. Else If command is COMMAND_UPDATE_RECORD Then call IndexableTable.update(Param[],Param[]).
        Specified by:
        run in interface Runnable
